    <abstract>
      <t>This document specifies an IP-based encapsulation for MPLS, called MPLS-in-UDP (User Datagram Protocol). Note that the MPLS-in-UDP encapsulation technology MUST only be deployed within a service provider network or networks of an adjacent set of co-operating service providers where the congestion control is not a concern.</t>
